x\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Persona is a clean, flexible and responsive photography WordPress theme with minimal looks. It is suitable for photographers, artists, bloggers, photo studios or photography agencies. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Using this theme, you can create any type of photography websites. You can showcase your rich content and media in unique and beautiful ways. You can also create portfolios sites, art galleries sites, or you can create a convenient online store to sell your works and valuable images &amp; photos.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>It supports popular plugins such as Contact Form 7, WooCommerce, Elementor, <a href=\"https://themebeez.com/plugins/\" target=\"_blank\" aria-label=\"UGAAM (opens in a new tab)\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"rank-math-link\">UGAAM</a>, etc. It is packed with all the photography components and it is fully functional to make your site better. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Persona is one of the best photography WordPress themes having 7 different homepage layout. Plus it has other 24 templates that will help you to create an awesome photography website. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3> Features </h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Responsive &amp; Retina Ready</li><li>SEO friendly </li><li>Easy Color Management</li><li>High Speed &amp; Clean Code</li><li>One-Click Demo Install</li><li>600+ Google Fonts</li><li>Extensive Documentation</li><li>Translation Ready</li><li>Clean &amp; Minimal Design</li><li>WooCommerce Compatible </li><li>Advanced Side Menu</li><li>7 Different Homepages</li><li>24 more templates with different designs</li><li>Supports Elementor, Contact Form 7 and other popular plugins.</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/persona-wordpress-photography-portfolio-and-blog-theme/19225817\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Persona</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>ETUDES</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Etudes-Screen_Shot-1024x652.png\" alt=\"Etudes Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7336\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Etudes-Screen_Shot-1024x652.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Etudes-Screen_Shot-300x191.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Etudes-Screen_Shot-768x489.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Etudes-Screen_Shot.png 1332w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Etudes has an amazing sharp design. It is a photography WordPress theme that is perfect for bloggers and photographers.  It showcases your content such as photos, images, paintings, drawings, etc without diminishing the real value of your work. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Its design looks gorgeous and can be used for creating professional photography sites. If you are an enthusiast and doing photography for fun then it is also for you. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It is a fully customizable theme and it is easy to use. There are over 600+ google fonts in this theme and it consists of easily manage the color options. It has a high-speed performance and advanced side menu. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>This theme contains numerous photo galleries that help to display your image, photos or contents in the best way possible. You will be able to show your work in different design options such as grid, masonry, slider, items filtering, ribbon, flow, blogging, etc. Therefore it is one of the best photography WordPress themes for photographers and bloggers. </p>\n\n\n\n<h3> Features </h3>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>Quality code &amp; Optimized for SEO</li><li>High-Speed Performance</li><li>Responsive &amp; Retina Ready</li><li>Amazing Sharp Designs</li><li>Advanced Typography</li><li>Extensive Documentation </li><li>Advanced Side Menu</li><li>6  Home Page Variants</li><li>Unlimited Number of Custom Portfolio Pages</li><li>FullScreen Blog Layout</li><li>Easy Color Management</li><li>Outstanding Support</li></ul>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"button-block\">\n<a class=\"btn-general\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themeforest.net/item/premium-photography-wordpress-theme-etudes/17129959\" target=\"_blank\">Details/Downloads Etudes</a>\n\n<a class=\"btn-general get-hosting\" rel=\"dofollow noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/best-wordpress-hosting-compared/\" target=\"_blank\">Get Hosting</a>\n</div>\n\n\n\n<hr class=\"wp-block-separator\"/>\n\n\n\n<h2>AZALEA</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large theme-image\"><img src=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Azalea-Screen_Shot-1024x665.png\" alt=\"Azalea Screen_Shot.png\" class=\"wp-image-7337\" srcset=\"https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Azalea-Screen_Shot-1024x665.png 1024w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Azalea-Screen_Shot-300x195.png 300w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Azalea-Screen_Shot-768x499.png 768w, https://themebeez.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/01/Azalea-Screen_Shot.png 1350w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Azalea is one of the best photography WordPress themes for fashion. It is the perfect theme for creating fashion-related photography websites and it is best for fashion photographers. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>It has 12 beautiful homepage layouts that are completely customizable on your style. You will be able to create your own fashion website in no time without having the knowledge of coding.  In this theme, There are multiple portfolio and gallery layouts styles that you can choose from to showcase your work. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>You can also use this theme for blogging purpose and it consists of multiple blogging lay